@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="container-header text-center mb-4">
        <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="card mb-3">
        <div class="card-body">
            <p>Your privacy is important to us. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.</p>

            <h5>Information We Collect:</h5>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Registration Information</strong>: When you register on our forum, we collect your username, email address, and password.</li>
                <li><strong>Profile Information</strong>: You may provide additional information in your profile, such as a profile picture and bio.</li>
                <li><strong>Posts and Comments</strong>: We collect the content you post and the comments you make.</li>
                <li><strong>Usage Data</strong>: We collect data about how you use the forum, such as the pages you visit and the actions you take.</li>
            </ul>

            <h5>How We Use Your Information:</h5>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>To Provide and Improve Our Services</strong>: We use your information to operate and enhance our forum.</li>
                <li><strong>To Communicate with You</strong>: We may use your email address to send you updates and important notifications.</li>
                <li><strong>To Ensure Security</strong>: We use your information to help maintain the security of our forum.</li>
            </ul>

            <h5>Data Protection:</h5>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Access Control</strong>: Only authorized personnel have access to your personal information.</li>
                <li><strong>Encryption</strong>: We use encryption to protect your data in transit and at rest.</li>
                <li><strong>User Control</strong>: You can manage your personal information through your account settings.</li>
            </ul>

            <h5>Third-Party Services:</h5>
            <p>We may use third-party services to help operate our forum. These services are required to adhere to our privacy standards.</p>

            <h5>Changes to This Policy:</h5>
            <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes.</p>

            <h5>Contact Us:</h5>
            <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at support@italyforum.com.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
